12 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
13 SECTION 1. There is hereby created in the State Treasury a
14 revolving fund for the Oklahoma Department of Career and Technology
15 Education to be designated the "Oklahoma Workforce Education
16 Partnership Revolving Fund". The fund shall be a continuing fund,
17 not subject to fiscal year limitations, and shall consist of all
18 monies received by the Oklahoma Department of Career and Technology
19 Education from monies appropriated or apportioned by the Legislature
20 and gifts, donations, and bequests. All monies accruing to the
21 credit of said fund are hereby appropriated and may be budgeted and
22 expended by the Oklahoma Department of Career and Technology
23 Education for the purpose of expanding career technology education
24 as determined by the Oklahoma Department of Career and Technology
